      "text": [
        " أَبُو اَلْحَسَنِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"إِنَّ اَللَّهَ تَبَارَكَ وَ تَعَالَى إِذَا أَرَادَ بِعَبْدٍ خَيْراً لَمْ يُمِتْهُ حَتَّى يُرِيَهُ اَلْخَلَفَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4690 - Abu al-Hasan (as) said:\n\"Indeed, when Allah (swt), the Blessed and Exalted, intends good for a servant, He (swt) does not cause him to die until He (swt) shows him (the believer) his successor.\""
        ]
      }
    },
